attributes.description: RHI Magnestia India ltd earlier known as Orient Refractories Limited (ORL) is in the business of manufacturing and marketing special refractory products, systems and services to the steel industry in India and Globally. It is a market leader for special refractories in India and has many global customers for its international quality products.[1]
